Paper: hep-th/9405068

Date: 1994-05-10

Title: Quenched Random Graphs

Authors: C. Bachas, C. de Calan and P.M.S. Petropoulos

Comments: 9 pages, report CPTH-A264.1093

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A27 (1994) 6121-6128

Spin models on quenched random graphs are related to many importantoptimization problems. We give a new derivation of their mean-field equationsthat elucidates the role of the natural order parameter in these models.